Meet <b>Sara</b>, our Citizen of the Week!<br><br>A neighbor of last week's Featured Citizen, Sara lives at <a href='/home/?user=saraelizabeth'>23514 Bear Mountain View</a> in Westridge. Her very festive house is easily recognizable as you're walking through the neighborhood. A resident of Millsberry since June 7, 2005, Sara always invites people to stop by and say hello.<br><br>You should definitely check out her house. With tons of bright colors and funky furniture combinations, her rooms make you feel instantly at home. Enjoying the soft couches and plentiful stuffed animals, you'll find it hard to leave!<br><br>Sara loves animals (she chose to live on Bear Mountain View, after all), and likes to visit the Pet Palace [link] to play with and feed the animals that are for sale. She encourages Rosie Ruiz to play music in the store, though Rosie isn't sure if the animals like rap and techno, two genres Sara really enjoys.<br><br>Send Sara a package or a greeting card and you might find you've got something in common. Thanks for being a good citizen, Sara, and congratulations on being named Citizen of the Week! </div>
